This is Sheriff Zhao
from the local station.

00:33:18.680 --> 00:33:20.160
- Chief Liu.
- Thanks for your work.

00:33:20.400 --> 00:33:22.270
That guy should still be in this town.

00:33:22.400 --> 00:33:24.600
Please have your men work some overtime.

00:33:24.600 --> 00:33:25.600
Don't worry, Chief Liu.

