Where's Uncle Danshun?

00:33:27.600 --> 00:33:30.360
Aren't we waiting for him?

00:33:30.710 --> 00:33:31.680
Be good, Mengmeng.

00:33:31.880 --> 00:33:32.880
Uncle Danshun...

00:33:33.600 --> 00:33:35.470
He'll come find us in a bit.

