How dare you lock me out?

00:37:54.030 --> 00:37:55.880
You useless thing, just like your mom.

00:37:55.880 --> 00:37:57.760
Neither of you can do anything.

00:37:58.360 --> 00:37:59.760
You got a death wish, huh?

00:38:00.400 --> 00:38:01.240
Did you hear me?

00:38:01.510 --> 00:38:02.550
